Ammo Drop		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat															PRESKILL:1,Sleight of Hand=1	PREWEAPONPROF:1,Sling,Sling Staff (Halfling),Sling (Double)	DESC:Your coordination is so perfect that you can simply drop ammunition from your hand at the exact moment required for it to fall into an open sling as your twirl it around.								SOURCEPAGE:p.23	BENEFIT:You can load a sling or one end of a double sling with one hand as a swift action or move action. This does not provoke an attack of opportunity.
Halfling Slinger	CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat								PRERACE:1,Halfling,RACESUBTYPE=Halfling																DESC:You have honed your racial talent for slingcraft.																					BONUS:COMBAT|TOHIT.Sling|1|TYPE=Racial	SOURCEPAGE:p.23	BENEFIT:You gain a +1 racial bonus on attack rolls made using a sling.
Juggle Load		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ammo Drop																							DESC:Your fingers are so nimble that reloading your sling is almost effortless for you.																							SOURCEPAGE:p.23	BENEFIT:You can load a sling or double sling as a free action. This does not provoke attacks of opportunity. This feat allows you to fire your sling as many times in a full attack action as you could attack if you were using a bow.
Large Target	CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat																				PREWEAPONPROF:1,Sling,Sling Staff (Halfling),Sling (Double)	DESC:The larger a creature is, the easier you find it to strike a vulnerable spot when attacking with a sling.																			SOURCEPAGE:p.23	BENEFIT:Your attacks with all kinds of slings add a +1 bonus on damage rolls for every size category your opponent is larger than you. For example, if you are Small and your opponent Large (a difference of two sizes), you gain a +2 damage bonus. This is considered precision damage and is not multiplied on a critical hit.
Whip-Slinger	CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat																				PREWEAPONPROF:1,Sling,Sling Staff (Halfling),Sling (Double)	DESC:You can use your sling as a sap to make attacks of opportunity.																										SOURCEPAGE:p.23	BENEFIT:When wielding a sling, double sling, or halfling sling staff, you threaten areas around you as normal and can make attacks of opportunity with the sling into these threatened areas. The sling deals 1d4 nonlethal bludgeoning damage (1d6 for a Medium wielder), threatens a critical hit on a 20, and deals x2 damage on a critical hit. If the sling isn't loaded with ammunition when you make an attack of opportunity, you take a -4 penalty on the attack roll.


###Block: Halfling Jinx Feats
